{"tid":219662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向劉小麗掟鞋　男子緩刑","createTime":"2017-04-27T11:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T13:19:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3095e24474649bc2ad46fa8664de31ba2f489b50","tid":219662,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20003194&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20003194%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170427&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGEzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7fb256dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20003194%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170427&h=d7667ab1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20003194&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170427</a><br />\n<br />\n向劉小麗掟鞋　男子緩刑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n被告（右二）案發當日被工作人員要求穿回波鞋及離場。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】育有6名子女的綜援漢去年10月出席維園舉行的《城市論壇》，趁小休期間向講台上的立法會議員劉小麗掟鞋。綜援漢昨承認普通襲擊罪，求情稱因不滿劉發言時「怨國家怨政府但不怨她自己」才衝動犯案，現已知錯，但表明無力付罰款，最後獲判入獄兩周，緩刑18個月。<br />\n<br />\n離庭爆粗罵記者<br />\n<br />\n被告黃大康（61歲）有暴力案底，律師求情稱，被告與妻均沒工作，靠綜援為生，育有3子3女，最年幼的僅11歲，被告本身有心臟、糖尿和高血壓問題，表明無力支付罰款，要求法庭判緩刑。<br />\n裁判官指香港有言論及表達自由，即使意見不合亦不應施以暴力，罰款未足以反映嚴重性，考慮被告年老有病，決定以緩刑處理。<br />\n被告昨答辯時，法庭明顯加強保安，被告有4名庭警及保安陪伴在側，又送他離開，他甫離庭即爆粗鬧記者：「影乜X嘢呀影！」<br />\n案發於去年10月30日，當日《城市論壇》討論退休法官胡國興參選特首，被告在小休期間離座走向劉小麗，脫下右邊波鞋掟向劉，擊中劉左前臂及胸口，之後離開，大會報警。被告翌日自首。<br />\n案件編號：ESCC1220/17<br />\n■記者蔡少玲<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n劉小麗案發後展示左前臂被掟傷致紅腫。"},{"pid":"5478be8ed8d8235af25a407b715f2e968f940ac3","tid":219662,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170427/large/27ls2p2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170427%2Flarge%2F27ls2p2e.jpg&h=fb2587e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0aac771ab37b2fda4647637df5b55e91de512000","tid":219662,"uid":51436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:13:43.000Z","msg":"胡師父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1ff8a98264bdc4af8186bb2ae371fa78a5efc2","tid":219662,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>胡師父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8a4cb76b9b5d49cb26d05b69d2d59adcef3b1a","tid":219662,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"超級蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75821f77cfa9099e95490ebaac13eca9a217be77","tid":219662,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3b923c21007d24818c821092350ea8b6e1a3dc","tid":219662,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:45:05.000Z","msg":"被告與妻均沒工作，靠綜援為生，育有3子3女，最年幼的僅11歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無錢生六個 香港人養"},{"pid":"2d36dc1a52bd634d4520debf95a41c7f9fabfdb5","tid":219662,"uid":93904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"被告與妻均沒工作，靠綜援為生<br />\n社會垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28653540a6ae4662262f2a4e6cded29ff62a94ae","tid":219662,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa433d728888b02e04c49a2f83b5284a4a94aef8","tid":219662,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被告與妻均沒工作，靠綜援為生，育有3子3女，最年幼的僅11歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無錢生六個 香港人養</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人要養呢班廢物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}